 Galvatron stopped. He thought....ah what the hell. He blasted off and landed 
near where he could still sence her signature. he went into his robot mode 
less intimidateing then a big silver dragon and put a smile on his face. 
"Hello Darkmouse. Please come out where I can see you. MY weapons are down 
scan for yourself." They actualy were he knew that was the only way she'd 
come out.
